    <section id="english">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>Slack Markdown Viewer collects minimal information necessary to provide the service:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Uploaded Markdown Files:</strong> Content of .md files uploaded to Slack channels where the app is installed</li>
          <li><strong>Workspace Authentication Tokens:</strong> OAuth tokens required for app functionality</li>
          <li><strong>Basic Workspace Information:</strong> Workspace ID and name for installation management</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="highlight">
          <p><strong>We do NOT collect:</strong> Personal information, user profiles, message content (other than .md files), or browsing history.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>The collected information is used solely for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Rendering markdown files into HTML format</li>
          <li>Providing shareable links to rendered content</li>
          <li>Maintaining app functionality within your Slack workspace</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>3. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Rendered Content:</strong> Automatically deleted after 24 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Authentication Tokens:</strong> Stored securely while the app is installed</li>
          <li><strong>Upon App Removal:</strong> All data associated with your workspace is immediately deleted</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <div class="highlight">
          <p><strong>We do NOT share any data with third parties.</strong></p>
        </div>
        <p>Your data remains on our servers and is never sold, transferred, or shared with external services.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
          <li>Secure storage of authentication tokens</li>
          <li>Automatic data expiration and cleanup</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Uninstall the app at any time, which will delete all associated data</li>
          <li>Request information about your stored data</li>
          <li>Request data deletion by contacting us</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

